text: Aleksandr Mishchenko (born 30 July 1997) is a German-Kyrgyzstani footballer who plays for Dordoi Bishkek in the Kyrgyzstan League and Kyrgyzstan national football team as a defender. ==Career== ===Club=== ===International=== Mishchenko made his debut for Kyrgyzstan national football team in a friendly match on 11 June 2019 against Palestine. ==Career statistics== ===International=== Statistics accurate as of match played 14 November 2019 {| class="wikitable" style="text-align:center" |- !colspan=3|Kyrgyzstan national team |- !Year!!Apps!!Goals |- |2019||3||0 |- !Total||3||0 |} ==Honours== Dordoi Bishkek * Kyrgyzstan Cup: 2017 * Kyrgyzstan Super Cup: 2019 == References == ==External links== * Category:1997 births Category:Living people Category:Kyrgyzstan international footballers Category:Kyrgyzstani footballers Category:FC Dordoi Bishkek players Category:Association football defenders Category:Kyrgyzstani people of Russian descent Category:German people of Russian descent Category:German people of Kyrgyzstani descent
